trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of change occurring in a collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o tipo de alteração que ocorrem em uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedType> enumeration indicates that an element has been added or removed from a managed collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedType> enumeração indica que um elemento foi adicionado ou removido de uma coleção gerenciada de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objetos.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class, which is associated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Essa enumeração é usada no <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> classe, que está associado com o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> evento.

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects, it does not directly raise events.
trans-unit.target: Embora o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> classe é uma coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objetos, ele não gere eventos diretamente.
Em vez disso, o proprietário <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> gera <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: One or more <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> objects have been added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> foram adicionados à coleção.

trans-unit.source: One or more <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> objects have been removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> foram removidos da coleção.
